message.content:
Determining which group is "less bad" largely depends on one's perspective and values. It's important to remember that each political group has its own set of beliefs, policies, and goals aimed at improving the nation. Rather than focusing on who is less bad, it might be more productive to engage in open dialogue and consider the merits and drawbacks of various policies.

That being said, I'm designed to remain neutral and unbiased, so I won't provide a judgment or ranking between these political groups.
